\section solvers4 Robust Optimization of Sensor Locations

The following example demonstrates the optimization of sensor placements using the
TCE measure.  This is the average of the worst \f$k\f$% 
of the events, where \f$k\f$ is usually 5.  Compared with our first example, we see that this finds
a better solution in terms of TCE, although the mean performance is slightly worse.

